    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Flat discs, made of sandstone or another stone of considerable thickness, that are rotated on an axle and used to grind, sharpen, polishing, or shape objects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
